Subject: [PATCH] drm/display: Fix building with GCC 15
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: a500f3751d3c861be7e4463c933cf467240cca5d
